{"tid":2246193,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［北歐國際線］芬蘭暫停與港引渡協議","createTime":"2020-10-17T00:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T00:56:36.000Z","uid":65139,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9802142a99842a021fdb55c94cac065cd499c90c","tid":2246193,"uid":65139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T00:22:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3323930\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3323930&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24haoxckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=696c47fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3323930&h=c3b0548f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3323930</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕芬蘭總統尼尼斯托（Sauli Niinisto）16日表示，為因應香港國安法的實施，正式中止與香港的引渡協議。先前英語圈國家「五眼聯盟」已率先暫停與香港的引渡協議。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，芬蘭政府公報16日指出，尼尼斯托總統已經批准司法部的這項提案，稱由於今天夏天生效的港版國安法，中國對香港的控制進一步加強，香港的法律地位不再明確，與香港的引渡協議不再適用。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，芬蘭政府公報16日指出，尼尼斯托總統已經批准司法部的這項提案，稱由於今天夏天生效的港版國安法，中國對香港的控制進一步加強，香港的法律地位不再明確，與香港的引渡協議不再適用。<br />\n<br />\n自從港版國安法實施後，許多國家相繼中止與香港的引渡協議，包含「五眼聯盟」的美國、澳洲、加拿大、英國及紐西蘭，以及德國和法國。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7efWduB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7efWduB.png&h=6a8eddb0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rt2YrPB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRt2YrPB.png&h=84bc3f9d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2nY46PC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2nY46PC.png&h=1f42c435&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"757671e251f21955e0ee66885f61b3f9a235933e","tid":2246193,"uid":60881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T00:23:22.000Z","msg":"gogogogog"},{"pid":"fa521f10038c7b6114cee8f524e47376c7cf35b7","tid":2246193,"uid":65139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"